    AZCategoryAdapter
    AZCategoryAdapter implements the adapter for the RecyclerView in AZCategoryFragment.

    Provides and holds a reference to the CardView used in the RecyclerView.

    AZCategoryFragment implements the view for categories within the dictionary database.

    AZTermListFragment implements a ListFragment representation of all the terms categorized under a selected category.

    HistoryDatabaseHelper
    Implements the database for the history table.
    HistoryListFragment
    HistoryListFragment implements a list view of all the most recently viewed definitions.
    HomeFragment
    HomeFragment implements dozens of memes images as a banner.
    MainActivity
    The top-level activity that manages the navigation between fragments and implements the view for the entire application.
    ResultActivity
    Handles the intent that performs a term search.
    SplashActivity
    Displays a landing screen before the program launches.

Package edu.mills.cs115 Description

Implementation of the CS63 dictionary, switch. Created for Mills CS 115: Mobile Application Development, Spring 2017.
